ComicInfo.Summary:
Ally Or Spy? Far from his frozen northland home, barbarian Ranger Andacanavar tracks a friend's killer in the exotic land of Behren. His only lead is the fugitive harem girl Sagara, who may, in truth, be a deep cover spy. Hunting both is a demon djinn with the power to transform anyone's deepest desires into their darkest nightmares. The Crouching Tiger meets Arabian Nights action is fast and furious as the world once again trembles on the brink of a deadly DemonWar!
